{"tid":1604044,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我開咗個post叫大家十一朝早去會展踢春袋；而家我唔覺得可行，除非...","createTime":"2019-09-30T00:20:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T08:43:16.000Z","uid":108502,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fe0f1dd2237c5b9ebc20ca54e7c14edfc7a70f0a","tid":1604044,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:20:36.000Z","msg":"原post：十一春袋係朝早時分 行動唔可以晏晝先開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1598769\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1598769</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我提出喺十一儀式進行嘅同時喺會展外圍大戰，令場面變得極難睇，係極具象徵意義又可以踢中對家春袋嘅行動<br />\n<br />\n而家我依然係咁諗，但係經過928晚嘅大搜捕，同埋929嘅大規模鎮壓<br />\n加上七一朝早唔夠人做嘢導致大量義士身陷險境嘅先例，令我覺得十一朝早嘅場面會極之危險，而人手唔夠嘅話更加會令到好多手足出事<br />\n所以我覺得自己有責任開依個post放棄返自己嘅建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">除非？</span></span><br />\n除非今日內見返612去添馬公園野餐，或者811晚號召第二日塞機場嘅聲勢<br />\n令到全香港不論和勇都決定背水一戰，萬人頭班車殺入灣仔，甚至今晚已經出定港島<br />\n否則，唔夠人數下行動只會招致失敗，令勇武手足喺黑警戒嚴狀態下犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a5da5a1fe3cdc7ac7dd8d06f026518b86f5caf","tid":1604044,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:24:27.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"8fd1931aeef345d0e44777034867244040abdfef","tid":1604044,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:25:05.000Z","msg":"姐係齊齊較鬧鐘<br />\n聽朝一早起身大賀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5f248a8e9dcbebe0bfcb2b6e3e4a494cf8cd6b","tid":1604044,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:29:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f0f98e55cd1d6da924cbd8c38a6f49a538be8c0","tid":1604044,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fd1931aeef345d0e44777034867244040abdfef","tid":1604044,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim